A SEG Portal is an online platform provided by the Sarawak Government that serves as a centralized resource for accessing all Sarawak government services and information online. It offers a convenient way to find and use various government services, which are organized by topic. To access these services, you need to register for a Sarawak ID account.

SarawakID is your individual single-sign-on identity that allows you to securely access Sarawak Government digital services. It provides easy and secure access to various online government services. There are two versions: SarawakID for individual use and SarawakID Corp for corporations. To register, you can click the SarawakID Register button on any Sarawak Government website and follow the step-by-step process. You can verify your SarawakID account at a Service Sarawak Counter, Kiosk, or via eKYC Online or the eKYC Sarawak Gov Mobile App.
